lead_paragraph: Danny Willett withstood the pressure and made a 15-foot birdie putt on the final hole to win the Dubai Desert Classic title by one shot on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: Willett Wins Dubai Desert Classic With Birdie Putt on 18th
headline.main: Willett Wins Dubai Desert Classic With Birdie Putt on 18th
